==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Utia
<hw>U"ti*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any species of large West Indian rodents of the
genus <gen>Capromys</gen>, or <gen>Utia</gen>. In general appearance and
habits they resemble rats, but they are as large as rabbits.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Utica</ent>⟦br⟧
